            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>In nomine Domini. Cons[tat me] <persName key="#Priests #Monks"><name
                                ref="Richardus">Richardus</name></persName> g[ra]tja Dei <rs
                            key="#Priests">presbiter</rs> et <rs key="#Monks">monachus</rs> atque
                            <rs key="#Abbots">ab[bas</rs> r]egule <rs key="#Monasteries"
                            >mon(asterii)</rs>
                        <orgName key="#Monasteries" ref="#juridical_persons/1487">Sancti
                            [Apo]llinaris qui vocatur Novus</orgName> accepissem [et a]ccepi a vobis
                                <persName><name ref="Apollinaris">Apollinaris</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Rent_in_money">[pensio]nem</rs> pro <rs key="#Landed_possessions"
                            >tribus untjis in int(egro)</rs> que [sunt posite] in <rs key="#Fundi"
                            >fundo</rs> qui vocatur [<geogName
                            key="#Fundi #Landed_possessions #Rent_in_money" ref="#estates/2421"
                                ><placeName key="#Fundi #Landed_possessions #Rent_in_money"
                                >Colopedio</placeName></geogName> cum omni]bus sibi pertinentibus,
                            <rs key="#Fines">ter[ritorio]</rs>
                        <geogName key="#Fines" ref="#estates/2422"><placeName key="#Fines"
                                ref="#places/3515">Liviense</placeName></geogName>, <rs key="#Plebs"
                            >plebe</rs>
                        <orgName key="#Plebs" ref="#juridical_persons/1488">Sancte
                            Repara[te]</orgName>, q[u]as per <rs
                            key="#Libellus/precaria/emphyteusis">enfite[o]sin</rs> tener[e v]ideti[s
                        ad iu]re suprascripti mon(asterii) nostri, pro t[ransactis indi][tjoni]bus
                        usque [... et per] unaq(ue)que inditjone <rs key="#Rent_in_money">denarii
                            quinque tantum</rs>. Unde pro munimine vestro fetj vo[bis hoc
                        deacce][p]tum in mense martjo, i[nditjone ..., <placeName ref="#places/594"
                            >Ravenne</placeName>]. Ego Richard(us) [presbiter] et mon(achus) atq(ue)
                        [abbas mona]s(terii) S(an)c(t)i Apoll(inaris) q(ui) v(ocatur) Novo m(anu)
                        m(ea) s(ub)s(cripsi).</ab>
